        <name>Gulseth gruve</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoq1SyFm3IYia68WjSB6eLm1HYHCVz_X1qjcx0Pijdmts-XU0zfTFCWF9MlHIqOM9-82zLmgSVUN3e0kYNG6g7MyMaFydAfE73Rjlvz87GGj9DHJ73ZAx1rcZypOuzMMsfK2XGlsTGil3xDqCygefDN0lSFSJIiWytFrA9xOs1yhwuiWLU6NEesO2USfn0_icSVflMrpL9KUec0?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Posisjon: 59.2176115, 9.5522958<br>Informasjon: Skråsynk mot nord. 10 meter opp i lia skal det ligge en dagstrosse, men denne var ikke mulig å finne. Antagelig fylt av kvist og hageavfall. Ikke tilknyttet Fossum Jernverk men påbegynt 1903. Se bilde for mer info. Kilde: Alf Olav Larsen - Gruver og skjerp i Skien.<br>Nettside: https://www.skien.kommune.no/globalassets/bdk/kultur/kulturkontoret/85526-kultursti-arhus_1b.pdf<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoqIH8rVfvdF507gB6uibbuBtptIWpI8ChgG--Quv-Pn9CB7uxeLmitQcjzX-vRXF4UI2APNOmYTpJ5Y80uqAW6QSZ_-n9GIZwW4h1sPE7NcSELcwjpiFBkhdUrgRa5J2A-oRfNfX8E37Y8nnsoqyqFdVJRx6lApSW0KUEU8HCJUnFsVpD3P_PW-T_R-s-DQ_WoCyQ5mvL1rjg?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoquGOSv3NW3GP9H4sLEp057QPWutbz-3NvoIEoNGH_vtcz5jEcV95K2mj4h8pXZXqBAcZbOn40ulRt7ST6dZmILVnWpAPAB4r-KNfx-hWwyS17i90ePZ7aseNoKosrSvgX3wbwLEh-CB5pMZEnLoknj24pS2sO-RTB9-66cGxpaVTo0YpFI3CF4H3_0OzdkHxZKg39asukEjQ?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBopHAxYBjdUomqWUN5SuH1y9W0whH27EVmG93NLlhGdZBMnjNIa_-gXnyOYD1odQuf_uh7ZF-CCBCNcdJaoXG6lJIfMeQs1L0V2G5NiJYuGx1Ffy3AHld19OwaNE9PTJ1F0lW_lH8BvFbXRwopRH88ltI37oO1LxPMSmzcepCo-9g5v9O6XOrh8kEFViwGDdRkOADPzeJGHH_Q?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
