        <name>Kors i fjellet</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoqC0tFmX2aMEZ3g9mMYX5eeTai_RS9db9yOsNotS2KI8-P95DWwrXseBcVLrwBZyV1gXwk4neoNC3FI4leS4c8JrDuaAgzlZx6H1rcV00awQxjV823f5zCKf5IBSCZdlp-IZqEYDoAlr2K71DnGkuluYOyvSGBqFJSIw4C9snSLsViuP74X6kkcG3hULqfQBfVyySca2hP9Nb4?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Posisjon: 59.2377823, 9.5436826<br>Informasjon: Slike kors var det vanlig å hogge inn i nærheten av gruvene. De tjente som fastmerker, «meter riks-tegn», når gruvene skulle måles med tanke på uttatt malmmengde og skattlegging.<br>Nettside: https://photos.app.goo.gl/SkPQzkgqQ3E6zR7n6 og https://photos.app.goo.gl/ZKktL6ESvvG6rdcN9<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBopKtb9Q3S_xaNnkJi682KAjedhxcAfjHlVLzd5lkQy-VD28Py_myyueNfZM2TrA3-GZWq6POsMd0PKar3HBkzdmo7TPcVtc4IYahJsrNwJALrj5SMtsAJzyXbmPOMvM5ivnAhW0pTal03SyBw9GAx7kSD0gQke3da_Y7AyMePShT1zpnHwmNGH8CP4fe3qi3lS2heqxDuXeVB8?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoqfwca7_EoZIR111QW8P9zzfAsy9TK10-5TQunO5lzI2gGEMedaZS5512ZawJ91aUBOfpxqIw-JfyZ8Bvf-QTYTd4uycDbkcwCKBPmpOfb_oDwBf862AqXjUdhb2UQYPUyEeH0wISy0qfnH_H5Rj_aEED9p03Ij5g5iUHdEE5quOsdlIaP2ccR26E1ric08kwIvvPR3hle9oQ?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
